|---|---|---|
| Indigo | `#6366F1` | ∑ |
| Amber | `#D97706` | ◈ |
| Emerald | `#059669` | ⬡ |
| Pink | `#DB2777` | ✦ |
| Blue | `#2563EB` | △ |
